data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Expedition_1
data.value: Expedition Timer show each expedition's remain time & expected end time. You can Add / Modify / Remove / Reset expedition item with top toolbar. Expedition Timer allow up to 5 items.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Expedition_2
data.value: This page allow edit expedition item for adding or editing. Select expedition type & time and time buff optioin. For finish editing, click top-right apply button.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Furnishing_1
data.value: Furnishing Timer show each furnishing complete time remaining & expected complete time. You can Add / Modify / Remove / Reset furnishing item with top toolbar. Furnishing Timer allow up to 5 items.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Furnishing_2
data.value: This page allow edit furnishing item for adding or editing. Select furnishing item rank and enter a note. Note is optional. For finish editing, click top-right apply button.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Gadget_1
data.value: Gadget Timer show each gadget's time remaining until reuse & expected reusable time. You can Add / Modify / Remove / Reset gadget item with top toolbar. Gadget Timer allow up to 500 items.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Gadget_2
data.value: This page allow edit gadget item for adding or editing. Select gadget type and enter a note. Note is optional. For finish editing, click top-right apply button.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_GatheringItem_1
data.value: Gathering Item Timer show each collectable item's recovery time remaining & expected recovery time. You can Add / Modify / Remove / Reset gathering item with top toolbar. Gathering Item Timer allow up to 500 items.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_GatheringItem_2
data.value: This page allow edit gathering item for adding or editing. Select gathering item type and enter a note. Note is optional. For finish editing, click top-right apply button.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_RealmCurrency_1
data.value: Realm Currency Timer screen show current RC count & fully restore expected time and etc. Also, you can perform quick edit with bottom buttons. However, the exact time is not shown in In-game, so there may be a difference.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_RealmCurrency_2
data.value: Realm Currency Timer can be set recovery rate and maximum size by setting Realm Rank and Trust Rank. You can adjust it according to your Realm environment.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_RealmCurrency_3
data.value: Realm Currency Timer also customize notification. You can set the RC ratio to receive notifications.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Resin_1
data.value: Resin Timer screen show current resin & fully restore expected time and etc. Also, you can perform quick calculation with bottom buttons.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Resin_2
data.value: Resin Timer contains bottom buttons to calculate resin. Press buttons which you want to calculation. <10, <20, <40 Buttons perform calculation less than 10, 20, 40 respectively.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Resin_3
data.value: Q.E. button allows user to adjust the number of resins without touching the time. It is very useful if there is a large difference in the number of resin in the in-game or if the result is not calculated quickly.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_Resin_4
data.value: Resin Timer also customize notification. You can set the resin count to receive notifications.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_TalentBook_1
data.value: Talent Book Timer show talent book item which you can get now. This timer reference game server and device timezone. You can select location with top toolbar. Also, you can see characters who use talent book with bottom button. This timer does not currently support notifications.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Timer_WeaponAscension_1
data.value: Weapon Ascension Timer show weapon ascension item which you can get now. This timer reference game server and device timezone. You can select location with top toolbar. This timer does not currently support notifications.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Widget_Resin_1
data.value: Resin Widget show now resin & expected fully restore time. You can run app by touching resin icon. Also, you can refresh resin status by touching layout except resin icon.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Widget_Resin_2
data.value: Resin Widget support simple layout widget. Simple Widget only show now resin. You can run app by touching resin icon. Also, you can refresh resin status by touching layout except resin icon.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Widget_TalentBook_1
data.value: Talent Book Widget show talent book which you can acquire on each location. Bottom buttons can change location. Also, you can see characters who use talent book by touching talent book image. You can refresh talent book status by touching layout except buttons and talent book image.

data.name: HowToUse_Category_Widget_WeaponAscension_1
data.value: Weapon Ascension Widget show weapon ascension material which you can acquire on each location. Bottom buttons can change location. You can refresh weapon ascension material status by touching layout except buttons and material image.
